Package: WARPqpcr
Type: Package
Title: Analyzes qPCR Data and Makes Plots for Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: S. Carson Callahan <scot.c.callahan@uth.tmc.edu>
Maintainer: S. Carson Callahan <scot.c.callahan@uth.tmc.edu>
Description: Provides functionality for analyzing qPCR data using the dCT and ddCT methods and 
    generating plots of results. This package also contains functions for finding the most stable
    housekeeping gene from a group of possible genes.
